(26, 0, 2, '3D rejuvenation', '3D rejuvenation', '2017-04-03 16:49:19', 0, '26logo.png', '', '', '26icon.png', '<p>Thermopeel MRF is a multifunctional platform providing effective treatment of wrinkles, hyperkeratosis, acne and enlarged pores, thickened skin, hyperpigmentation marks, stretch marks, scars and baldness.</p>\r\n', '<p>Thermopeel MRF is a multifunctional platform providing effective treatment of wrinkles, hyperkeratosis, acne and enlarged pores, thickened skin, hyperpigmentation marks, stretch marks, scars and baldness.</p>\r\n', ''),
