(33, 0, 2, 'BeautyLab redefines the world of beauty and wellbeing', 'BeautyLab redefines the world of beauty and wellbeing', '2017-04-03 17:07:40', 0, '33logo.png', '', '', '33icon.png', '<p>Its innovative technologies grant unique experiences with excellent, safe, painless and quick results on every area of face and body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> With BeautyLab your aesthetician can detox the skin of your face with a cavitational micropeeling treatment or can tone your legs by reducing cellulite.</p>\r\n', '<p>Its innovative technologies grant unique experiences with excellent, safe, painless and quick results on every area of face and body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> With BeautyLab your aesthetician can detox the skin of your face with a cavitational micropeeling treatment or can tone your legs by reducing cellulite.</p>\r\n', '');

