(17, 17, '<p><strong>X-Lase includes a Calibrated Pulsed Light (CPL) system combined with Nd:YAG laser, therefore resulting a very versatile platform because Erbium and Q-Switched can be included.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPL Calibrated Pulsed Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The new CPL MotionSpeed technology is a great breakthrough in patient comfort: the procedure speeds and gives incomparable clinical results. In CPL Speed mode, X-Lase combines a powerful cooling system with calibrated pulsed light which enables penetrating the heating energy into the target chromophore while preserving the surrounding tissues. With this new MotionSpeed system the procedure is much faster with virtually constant power flow, with noteworthy improvement in the level of patient comfort, increased speed and effectiveness of the photo-epilation process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nd:YAG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Nd:YAG module guarantees an effective and safe laser treatment for hair removal, vascular lesions and hyperpigmentation marks on all skin types.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Q-Switched</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The beam penetrates the skin to reach the ink particles. The pigments absorb the light energy and are destroyed and eliminated by lymph system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Erbium:YAG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fractional Erbium laser technology is able to treat the deep and superficial layers of the skin, being highly effective for the treatment of facial lines and wrinkles, acne scarring, age spots, deep pigment, rough texture, redness, large pores and overall skin quality.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>X-Lase includes a Calibrated Pulsed Light (CPL) system combined with Nd:YAG laser, therefore resulting a very versatile platform because Erbium and Q-Switched can be included.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPL Calibrated Pulsed Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The new CPL MotionSpeed technology is a great breakthrough in patient comfort: the procedure speeds and gives incomparable clinical results. In CPL Speed mode, X-Lase combines a powerful cooling system with calibrated pulsed light which enables penetrating the heating energy into the target chromophore while preserving the surrounding tissues. With this new MotionSpeed system the procedure is much faster with virtually constant power flow, with noteworthy improvement in the level of patient comfort, increased speed and effectiveness of the photo-epilation process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nd:YAG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Nd:YAG module guarantees an effective and safe laser treatment for hair removal, vascular lesions and hyperpigmentation marks on all skin types.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Q-Switched</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The beam penetrates the skin to reach the ink particles. The pigments absorb the light energy and are destroyed and eliminated by lymph system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Erbium:YAG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fractional Erbium laser technology is able to treat the deep and superficial layers of the skin, being highly effective for the treatment of facial lines and wrinkles, acne scarring, age spots, deep pigment, rough texture, redness, large pores and overall skin quality.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>X-Lase is an important breakthrough in the treatment of a variety of skin and body imperfections.</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe simultaneous use of a Nd:YAG laser and an innovative calibrated pulsed light system (CPL) allows to solve various problems, such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- unwanted hair<br />\r\n- skin marks<br />\r\n- freckles<br />\r\n- ageing skin<br />\r\n- unsightly small veins<br />\r\n- enlarged pores<br />\r\n- acne<br />\r\n- rosacea<br />\r\n- reddened skin</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>The CPL handpiece</strong>&nbsp;is efficient and simple to use, the operator has easy access to the controls and all the user information is clearly displayed on the colour screen, including the energy level, the pulse duration, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Nd:YAG laser</strong>&nbsp;provides fast and effective hair removal treatment even on dark skins. The calibrated laser beam ensures the light to penetrate into the deepest follicles, while its slow absorption guarantees the preservation of the surrounding tissues in all skin types. Different spot spacers allow effective treatment even for the toughest hair, excellent results on treating vascular problems and skin blemishes.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>X-Lase is an important breakthrough in the treatment of a variety of skin and body imperfections.</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe simultaneous use of a Nd:YAG laser and an innovative calibrated pulsed light system (CPL) allows to solve various problems, such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- unwanted hair<br />\r\n- skin marks<br />\r\n- freckles<br />\r\n- ageing skin<br />\r\n- unsightly small veins<br />\r\n- enlarged pores<br />\r\n- acne<br />\r\n- rosacea<br />\r\n- reddened skin</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>The CPL handpiece</strong>&nbsp;is efficient and simple to use, the operator has easy access to the controls and all the user information is clearly displayed on the colour screen, including the energy level, the pulse duration, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Nd:YAG laser</strong>&nbsp;provides fast and effective hair removal treatment even on dark skins. The calibrated laser beam ensures the light to penetrate into the deepest follicles, while its slow absorption guarantees the preservation of the surrounding tissues in all skin types. Different spot spacers allow effective treatment even for the toughest hair, excellent results on treating vascular problems and skin blemishes.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>General specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cooling system: water, air<br />\r\nSkin cooling: Peltier<br />\r\nInterface: touchscreen LCD display 7&#39;&#39;<br />\r\nDimensions: 440x540x350 mm (LxDxH)<br />\r\nweight: 37 kg<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPower supply: 230 Vac 50/600 Hz<br />\r\nPotenza: 2.000 W (max)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nd:YAG Laser module</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nLaser type:&nbsp; Nd:YAG<br />\r\nWavelenght: 1064 nm<br />\r\nClass: 4<br />\r\nEnergy: up to 24 J (max)<br />\r\nPulse Duration: from 5 to 40 ms<br />\r\nRepetition rate: from 1 to 3 Hz<br />\r\nSpot Size: 2.5 &ndash; 4 - 5 - 7 - 10 mm<br />\r\nLaser emission control: Pedal<br />\r\nAiming Beam: Laser Pointer 1 mW @ 635 nm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>CPL (Calibrated Pulsed Light module)</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSource: xenon lamp&nbsp;<br />\r\nSpectrum of Emission: 410 - 1200 nm; 550 -1200nm; 550 - 950nm;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 755 -1200nm; 650 - 950nm; 695-1200nm;<br />\r\nImpulse energy: up to 27 J/cm2&nbsp;<br />\r\nPulse duration: from 5 to 60 ms<br />\r\nNumber of pulses: from 1 to 5<br />\r\nRepetition rate: Auto- 1,0s &ndash; 1,5s - 2 s (min.)<br />\r\nTreatment Area: 10,1 x 50 mm (5 cm2)<br />\r\nEmission control: Pedal and applicator button<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Q-Switched</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Laser type: CR:YAG<br />\r\nWavelenght: 1064 nm (532 nm with KTP lens)<br />\r\nClass: 4<br />\r\nEnergy: 2 J circa<br />\r\nDivergenza: 5 mrad<br />\r\nSingle impulse duration: 9 ns<br />\r\nSpot size: 2,5 - 50mm<br />\r\nRepetition rate: from 1 to 6 Hz</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>General specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cooling system: water, air<br />\r\nSkin cooling: Peltier<br />\r\nInterface: touchscreen LCD display 7&#39;&#39;<br />\r\nDimensions: 440x540x350 mm (LxDxH)<br />\r\nweight: 37 kg<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPower supply: 230 Vac 50/600 Hz<br />\r\nPotenza: 2.000 W (max)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nd:YAG Laser module</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nLaser type:&nbsp; Nd:YAG<br />\r\nWavelenght: 1064 nm<br />\r\nClass: 4<br />\r\nEnergy: up to 24 J (max)<br />\r\nPulse Duration: from 5 to 40 ms<br />\r\nRepetition rate: from 1 to 3 Hz<br />\r\nSpot Size: 2.5 &ndash; 4 - 5 - 7 - 10 mm<br />\r\nLaser emission control: Pedal<br />\r\nAiming Beam: Laser Po