(25, 25, '<p><strong>X-Light includes an independent Calibrated Pulsed Light &ndash; CPL, system.&nbsp;The versatile X-Light platform enables carrying out a wide range of procedures.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPL - Calibrated Pulsed Light Technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The new CPL MotionSpeed technology is a great breakthrough in patient comfort, procedure speed and gives incomparable clinical results. In CPL Speed mode, X-Light combines a powerful cooling system with calibrated pulsed light which, unlike traditional IPL systems, enables penetrating the heating energy into the target chromophore while preserving the surrounding tissues.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith this new MotionSpeed system the procedure is much faster with virtually constant power flow, with noteworthy improvement in the level of patient comfort and increased speed and effectiveness of the photo-depilation process.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>X-Light includes an independent Calibrated Pulsed Light &ndash; CPL, system.&nbsp;The versatile X-Light platform enables carrying out a wide range of procedures.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPL - Calibrated Pulsed Light Technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The new CPL MotionSpeed technology is a great breakthrough in patient comfort, procedure speed and gives incomparable clinical results. In CPL Speed mode, X-Light combines a powerful cooling system with calibrated pulsed light which, unlike traditional IPL systems, enables penetrating the heating energy into the target chromophore while preserving the surrounding tissues.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith this new MotionSpeed system the procedure is much faster with virtually constant power flow, with noteworthy improvement in the level of patient comfort and increased speed and effectiveness of the photo-depilation process.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>X-Light is an important breakthrough in the treatment of a variety of skin and body imperfections:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Unwanted hair<br />\r\n- Folliculitis<br />\r\n- Wrinkles&nbsp;<br />\r\n- Acne<br />\r\n- Enlarged pores<br />\r\n- Sun damage<br />\r\n- Age spots<br />\r\n- Vascular lesions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The number of treatments is determined according to the patient&rsquo;s age and the seriousness of the condition being treated. The results can be seen right after the first session.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>X-Light is an important breakthrough in the treatment of a variety of skin and body imperfections:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Unwanted hair<br />\r\n- Folliculitis<br />\r\n- Wrinkles&nbsp;<br />\r\n- Acne<br />\r\n- Enlarged pores<br />\r\n- Sun damage<br />\r\n- Age spots<br />\r\n- Vascular lesions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The number of treatments is determined according to the patient&rsquo;s age and the seriousness of the condition being treated. The results can be seen right after the first session.</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Lamp type</strong>: Xenon<br />\r\n	<strong>Source</strong>: pulsed light<br />\r\n	<strong>Spectrum of Emission</strong>: 550 -1200nm; 550 - 950nm; 650 - 950nm; 695 - 1200nm; 755 -1200nm; 420-1200nm;<br />\r\n	<strong>Pulse duration</strong>: 1-100ms<br />\r\n	<strong>Pulse Frequency</strong>: 1Hz<br />\r\n	<strong>Treated area</strong>: 50mm x 10mm (5cm2)<br />\r\n	<strong>Burst mode</strong>: 1-10 pulses - pulse delay 10-100 ms<br />\r\n	<strong>Energy density</strong>: 150 J<br />\r\n	<strong>System cooling</strong>: Water and Hair<br />\r\n	<strong>Skin cooling</strong>: Ice type integrated<br />\r\n	<strong>Interface</strong>: touch Screen LCD<br />\r\n	<strong>Dimensions</strong>: 600 x 560 x 360 mm<br />\r\n	<strong>Weight</strong>: 35 kg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Lamp type</strong>: Xenon<br />\r\n	<strong>Source</strong>: pulsed light<br />\r\n	<strong>Spectrum of Emission</strong>: 550 -1200nm; 550 - 950nm; 650 - 950nm; 695 - 1200nm; 755 -1200nm; 420-1200nm;<br />\r\n	<strong>Pulse duration</strong>: 1-100ms<br />\r\n	<strong>Pulse Frequency</strong>: 1Hz<br />\r\n	<strong>Treated area</strong>: 50mm x 10mm (5cm2)<