(29, 29, '<p><strong>Intratone is the most advanced body and face reshaping technology, employing the latest modulated biomedical currents into one safe and non-invasive system for body and facial contouring.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nIntratone have been proven in clinical tests to build muscle and strength, as well as improve endurance and aid in faster muscle recovery on a post event basis. Intratone&rsquo;s biomedical currents produce powerful muscle contractions through &ldquo;optimal&rdquo;, safe and comfortable electrical impulses delivered at the motor nerves surprisingly increasing the quality of the aesthetic results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on the treatment area, alectrical currents use different frequency cycles to stimulate different layers of muscle tissue, skin, fat, connective tissue, circulatory and lymph systems, to effectively slim, tighten, tone, lift, firm, shape and rejuvenate.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>Intratone is the most advanced body and face reshaping technology, employing the latest modulated biomedical currents into one safe and non-invasive system for body and facial contouring.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nIntratone have been proven in clinical tests to build muscle and strength, as well as improve endurance and aid in faster muscle recovery on a post event basis. Intratone&rsquo;s biomedical currents produce powerful muscle contractions through &ldquo;optimal&rdquo;, safe and comfortable electrical impulses delivered at the motor nerves surprisingly increasing the quality of the aesthetic results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on the treatment area, alectrical currents use different frequency cycles to stimulate different layers of muscle tissue, skin, fat, connective tissue, circulatory and lymph systems, to effectively slim, tighten, tone, lift, firm, shape and rejuvenate.</p>\r\n', '<p>It includes personalized programs for males and females, including self- adapting parameters and chance to work simultaneously on two patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p