eposits are drained through the lymphatic system, reducing the appearance of cellulite.</li>\r\n	<li>Stretch marks<br />\r\n	Fractional radiofrequency induces the skin to produce new collagen and elastin which generate new skin cells to repair itself; the skin becomes thicker, plumper and more youthful.</li>\r\n	<li>Firming<br />\r\n	Made possible through the tightening of the skin. With a delicate lifting effect, the treatment tones and firms treated areas, leaving the skin smoother, softer and younger-looking.</li>\r\n	<li>Toning<br />\r\n	The technologies used to tone body skin acts on the treated areas with gradual but visible results for a more defined silhouette.</li>\r\n	<li>Restoring circulation<br />\r\n	Stimulating circulation with localised treatments and targeted technologies, make it possible to reduce cellulite, while improving the elasticity and tone of the skin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Power supply: 100 to 230 Vac - 50/60 Hz<br />\r\n	Power consumption: 160 W (operating mode)<br />\r\n	Class and type: The BF<br />\r\n	Dimensions: 400 (W) x 400 (D) x 220 (H) mm<br />\r\n	Fuse Protection: 2x 250V 2AF<br />\r\n	Radiofrequency<br />\r\n	Rf: 500 kHz (sinusoidal wave signal modulated in amplitude)<br />\r\n	Power Provided RW (max): 50W<br />\r\n	RF mode operation: Continuous<br />\r\n	Electroporation<br />\r\n	Electroporation: 1 kHz (signal with DC component and AC amplitude modulated)<br />\r\n	Output power (max): 10W<br />\r\n	Detox / Peeling<br />\r\n	Working frequency: 25 kHz<br />\r\n	Maximum output power: &lt;10 W<br />\r\n	Size emission head (spatula): 35x30 mm approximately<br />\r\n	Operating mode: continuous<br />\r\n	Cavitation (aesthetics)<br />\r\n	Ultrasound: 28 KHz<br />\r\n	Nominal power: up to 100 Watts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Power supply: 100 to 230 Vac - 50/60 Hz<br />\r\n	Power consumption: 160 W (operating mode)<br />\r\n	Class and type: The BF<br />\r\n	Dimensions: 400 (W) x 400 (D) x 220 (H) mm<br />\r\n	Fuse Pro