('201702230110', 'P', 'Renlive Presents Liposnell', 'Renlive Presents Liposnell', '<h3><strong>LIPOSLIM&nbsp;</strong>and&nbsp;<strong>LIPODREN&nbsp;</strong>INTENSIVE TREATMENTS PROTOCOLS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;LIPODREN</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nINTENSIVE DRAINING, DETOXIFYING TREATMENT REDUCING&nbsp;<strong>WATER RETENTION AND EDEMATOUS CELLULITE&nbsp;</strong>FOR LEGS, HIPS, ABDOMEN, ARMS AND BUTTOCKS.<br />\r\nPREPARE THE COUCH WITH CARTENE BED SHEET<br />\r\nPRODUCTS NEEDED:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSATURATED SOLUTION WITH&nbsp;<strong>RENLIVE&nbsp;</strong>DEAD SEA SALTS (SEE BELOW NOTE)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>BODY PEEL</strong><br />\r\n<strong>SPRAY MIST</strong><br />\r\n<strong>SPRAY THERMOFORCE</strong><br />\r\n<strong>VIAL NEOCELL</strong><br />\r\n<strong>LIPOSNELL</strong><br />\r\n<strong>BODY SERUM</strong><br />\r\n<strong>COTTON OR MICROFIBER PANTYHOSE 40/50 DEN ( POSSIBLY LIGHT COLORED )</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n1) cleanse the areas to be treated with<strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>BODY PEEL&nbsp;</strong>or&nbsp;<strong>SPRAY MIST</strong>. Cleansing with peeling is recommended at least at the first treatment, in the following sessions it can be alternated with the spray mist. This frequency depends on the thickness of the customer tissue;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2) apply&nbsp;<strong>SPRAY THERMOFORCE&nbsp;</strong>only on the abdomen, hips, buttocks and possibly on the lateral thigh side (only in the absence of telangiectasia) letting it be gently absorbed;<br />\r\n3) This product, specifically studied to create hyperemia, increases the vehiculation of the principal actives deeply and speeds up the metabolism of the tissues without causing excessive and annoying redness;<br />\r\n4) on the most affected areas apply the vial&nbsp;<strong>NEOCELL</strong>;<br />\r\n5) perform manual lymphatic drainage of abdomen, inguinal and popliteal ganglia;<br />\r\n6) apply with a brush a layer of&nbsp;<strong>LIPOSNELL&nbsp;</strong>enough to cover the affected areas;<br />\r\n7) let the customer wear the tights previously soaked in a saturated solution of<strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>DEAD SEA SALTS</strong>(for about 25/30 minutes)<br />\r\n8) once the time has ended remove the tights and apply&nbsp;<strong>BODY SERUM&nbsp;</strong>all over the body with lightly and gently.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNOTES:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLIPOSNELL is formulated with highly penetrating active ingredients, with an efficacy of immediate and deep absorption. It does not need, therefore, of special manual massage. If you want to increase the intensity of the result, immediately after its application and before applying the bandage it is possible to perform a manual draining of the whole area to be treated by adding a greater amount of product to facilitate the sliding.<br />\r\nThe product contains a derivative of a newly developed iodine that does not interfere on the thyroid but acts directly on adipocytes.<br />\r\nFor the bandage with Dead Sea salt, it&rsquo;s possible and even suggested to use cotton or microfiber tights (thickness 40 or 50), easily available on the market, replacing the traditional bandages that need a large amount of product, and also require costs and much more time for wrapping. In case of arms treatment it is possible to &quot;cut&quot; the tights at the top and at the tip.<br />\r\nFor greater comfort of the client it is recommended to cool down the solution saturated with Dead Sea salts before soaking the tights in. For those who dispose of towel warmer or microwave: soak the tights and warm them up for a period of time to NOT make them HOT. The panty is also easy to wash, disinfect, dries quickly and is reusable for the duration of the treatment program.<br />\r\nThe treatment&nbsp;<strong>LIPODREN&nbsp;</strong>increases its effectiveness in combination with the treatment with Perfect Press. In this case, perform the treatment till point 6, then let the customer wear the appropriate &quot;presso panty&quot; and let the treatment of presso-therapy rum for 25-30 minutes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>PREPARATION OF THE DEAD SEA SALT SATURATED SOLUTION</strong>:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1 LITRE OF HOT WATER<br />\r\n2HG AND A HALF OF THE RENLIVEDEAD SEA SALT<br />\r\nDissolve the salt in the water carefully<br />\r\nThe solution can be stored for the following days in a bottle<br />\r\nWishing to prepare a smaller quantity, decrease doses respecting the proportions<br />\r\nNB: the saturated solution works by osmosis in contact with the body. The time of action must not be less than 25/30 minutes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>LIPOSLIM</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nINTENSIVE REDUCING, SLIMMING, MODELLING TREATMENT FOR CELLULITE AND LOCALIZED ADIPOSITY.<br />\r\nSPECIFIC FOR LEGS, HIPS, ABDOMEN, ARMS AND GLUTEUS<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPREPARE THE COUCH WITH A CARTENE BED SHEET<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPRODUCTS NEEDED:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>BODY PEEL, SPRAY MIST, SPRAY THERMOFORCE, NEOCELL VIAL, LIPOSNELL, BODY MASK, BODY SERUM</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n1) cleanse the areas to be treated with BODY PEEL or SPRAY MIST. Cleansing with peeling is recommended at least at the first treatment, in the following sessions it can be alternated with the spray mist. This frequency depends on the thickness of the customer tissue;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2) apply&nbsp;<strong>SPRAY THERMOFORCE&nbsp;</strong>only on the abdomen, hips, buttocks and possibly on the lateral thigh side (only in the absence of telangiectasia) letting it be gently absorbed;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3) This product, specifically studied to create hyperemia, increases the vehiculation of the principal actives deeply and speeds up the metabolism of the tissues without causing excessive and annoying redness;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4) on the most affected areas apply the vial&nbsp;<strong>NEOCELL</strong>;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5) perform manual lymphatic drainage of abdomen, inguinal and popliteal ganglia;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6) apply with a brush a layer of&nbsp;<strong>LIPOSNELL&nbsp;</strong>enough to cover the affected areas;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n7) wait for a while and then apply a layer of<strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>BODY MASK&nbsp;</strong>on the affected areas, with cartene wrap and leave it on for 20 minutes;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n8) once the time has ended rinse the mask and apply gently&nbsp;<strong>BODY SERUM&nbsp;</strong>all over the body.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNOTES:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLIPOSNELL is formulated with highly penetrating active ingredients, with an efficacy of immediate and deep absorption. It does not need, therefore, of special manual massage. If you want to increase the intensity of the result, immediately after its application and before applying the bandage it is possible to perform a manual draining of the whole area to be treated by adding a greater amount of product to facilitate the sliding.</p>\r\n ', '<h3><strong>LIPOSLIM&nbsp;</strong>and&nbsp;<strong>LIPODREN&nbsp;</strong>INTENSIVE TREATMENTS PROTOCOLS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;LIPODREN</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nINTENSIVE DRAINING, DETOXIFYING TREATMENT REDUCING&nbsp;<strong>WATER RETENTION AND EDEMATOUS CELLULITE&nbsp;</strong>FOR LEGS, HIPS, ABDOMEN, ARMS AND BUTTOCKS.<br />\r\nPREPARE THE COUCH WITH CARTENE BED SHEET<br />\r\nPRODUCTS NEEDED:<br />\r\n<br />\r\