sk and apply gently&nbsp;<strong>BODY SERUM&nbsp;</strong>all over the body.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNOTES:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLIPOSNELL is formulated with highly penetrating active ingredients, with an efficacy of immediate and deep absorption. It does not need, therefore, of special manual massage. If you want to increase the intensity of the result, immediately after its application and before applying the bandage it is possible to perform a manual draining of the whole area to be treated by adding a greater amount of product to facilitate the sliding.</p>\r\n', '2017-02-22 00:00:00', 'A'),
('201702230138', 'P', 'Cryoliposculpt candidate for the i-NOVO', 'Cryoliposculpt candidate for the i-NOVO', '<p>Biotec Italia is happy and proud to announce that&nbsp;<a href="http://www.cryoliposculpt.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt</strong></a>&nbsp;has been selected for the&nbsp;<strong>MedicalExpo i-NOVO Awards</strong>&nbsp;in the&nbsp;<strong>TECH category</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>The i-NOVO Tech award will be given to products that demonstrate&nbsp;<strong>novel use of technology</strong>, whether it be the invention of a new technology, a technological innovation in the fabrication process (automatic or manual), the use of advanced technology to improve a design, the application of existing technologies in a new domain, the integration of several new technologies in one product or a completely innovative concept.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>ABOUT I-NOVO AWARDS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>i-NOVO Awards is at its first edition and is&nbsp;<strong>organised by MedicalExpo</strong>&nbsp;among its virtual exhibitors. It will&nbsp;<strong>identify and reward products that improve the industry&rsquo;s standards through innovation</strong>.&nbsp;<br />\r\nDuring&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://biotecitalia.com/en/news/item/biotec-italia-at-medica-2015-in-duesseldorf" target="_blank">Medica</a></strong>&nbsp;all the candidates will display&nbsp;<strong>dedicated promotional material</strong>&nbsp;at their booth to highlight their products&#39; participation.<br />\r\nThe other two categories further to Tech are the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The i-NOVO&nbsp;<strong>Design award</strong>&nbsp;will recognize products that take a step outside of the box. Products in this category could integrate current design trends, be visually unique, demonstrate exceptional attention to ergonomics or propose an innovative solution for an emerging need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The i-NOVO&nbsp;<strong>Eco award</strong>&nbsp;will be attributed to products that lessen or eliminate impact on the environment. Such products might have a sustainable manufacturing process or lower embodied energy and may use biodegradable, recyclable or reusable materials. Products in this category may also have a durable product life cycle and reduced energy consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>ABOUT FUSIOMED CRYOLIPOSCULPT</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt is a&nbsp;<strong>non-invasive fat removal procedure</strong>&nbsp;that works on the principle of a process referred as&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;selective cryolysis&rdquo;</em>.&nbsp;<br />\r\nSubcutaneous fat cells (fat cells situated between the skin and muscle layers) are more vulnerable to the effects of low temperature than&nbsp;<br />\r\nother surrounding tissues, and prolonged cooling of these fat cells can cause those cells to reduce in number, without damaging any of the close by tissues.<br />\r\nThese lipids are then transported by the lymphatic drainage system to be processed and eliminated through the body in the same way that fat from the food is&nbsp;<br />\r\neliminated. This process is very gradual, meaning that there is no danger of the lymphatic system being overloaded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt introduce a&nbsp;<strong>revolutionary procedure</strong>&nbsp;in medical aesthetic field.<br />\r\nThe cryoliposculpt device allows a&nbsp;<strong>dual treatment face-body</strong>. Infact, while undergoing a body cryoliposculpting, it allows a face treatment (RF, microneedling etc).<br />\r\nFusiomed Cryoliposculpt is a device&nbsp;<strong>able to treat different skin imperfection simultaneously</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>to meet both physicians and patients&#39; need at the same time</strong>.<br />\r\nThe&nbsp;<strong>Combo/Dual Treatment Technology</strong>&nbsp;allows to sculpt face and body at the same time, which is a truly revolutionary treatment method.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contouring the face while effectively reducing excess localized fat with Cryoliposculpt is now possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt:<br />\r\n- is a solution for face and body,&nbsp;<br />\r\n- allows to achieve different results at the same time,&nbsp;<br />\r\n- increase potential revenues and improve medical studios&#39; reputation,<br />\r\n- increases appointments booking,<br />\r\n- saves time for both physicians and patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Discover&nbsp;<strong>100% made in Italy</strong>&nbsp;technolgoies at Medica 2015, from 16th to 19th November, at&nbsp;<strong>HALL 11 STAND G69</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>ABOUT MEDICAL EXPO</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>MedicalExpo is a virtual exhibition of medical and sanitary market. Introduced in 2012, it has quickly established itself as the leading online resource for health professionals. With MedicalExpo, visitors can source and bookmark products, catch up on trends and directly contact manufacturers. It&rsquo;s a miniature eco-system dedicated to helping them do their job. It is powered by a group of experts that are passionate about innovation.</p>\r\n', '<p>Biotec Italia is happy and proud to announce that&nbsp;<a href="http://www.cryoliposculpt.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt</strong></a>&nbsp;has been selected for the&nbsp;<strong>MedicalExpo i-NOVO Awards</strong>&nbsp;in the&nbsp;<strong>TECH category</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>The i-NOVO Tech award will be given to products that demonstrate&nbsp;<strong>novel use of technology</strong>, whether it be the invention of a new technology, a technological innovation in the fabrication process (automatic or manual), the use of advanced technology to improve a design, the application of existing technologies in a new domain, the integration of several new technologies in one product or a completely innovative concept.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>ABOUT I-NOVO AWARDS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>i-NOVO Awards is at its first edition and is&nbsp;<strong>organised by MedicalExpo</strong>&nbsp;among its virtual exhibitors. It will&nbsp;<str