ess is very gradual, meaning that there is no danger of the lymphatic system being overloaded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt introduce a&nbsp;<strong>revolutionary procedure</strong>&nbsp;in medical aesthetic field.<br />\r\nThe cryoliposculpt device allows a&nbsp;<strong>dual treatment face-body</strong>. Infact, while undergoing a body cryoliposculpting, it allows a face treatment (RF, microneedling etc).<br />\r\nFusiomed Cryoliposculpt is a device&nbsp;<strong>able to treat different skin imperfection simultaneously</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>to meet both physicians and patients&#39; need at the same time</strong>.<br />\r\nThe&nbsp;<strong>Combo/Dual Treatment Technology</strong>&nbsp;allows to sculpt face and body at the same time, which is a truly revolutionary treatment method.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contouring the face while effectively reducing excess localized fat with Cryoliposculpt is now possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fusiomed Cryoliposculpt:<br />\r\n- is a solution for face and body,&nbsp;<br />\r\n- allows to achieve different results at the same time,&nbsp;<br />\r\n- increase potential revenues and improve medical studios&#39; reputation,<br />\r\n- increases appointments booking,<br />\r\n- saves time for both physicians and patients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Discover&nbsp;<strong>100% made in Italy</strong>&nbsp;technolgoies at Medica 2015, from 16th to 19th November, at&nbsp;<strong>HALL 11 STAND G69</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>ABOUT MEDICAL EXPO</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>MedicalExpo is a virtual exhibition of medical and sanitary market. Introduced in 2012, it has quickly established itself as the leading online resource for health professionals. With MedicalExpo, visitors can source and bookmark products, catch up on trends and directly contact manufacturers. It&rsquo;s a miniature eco-system dedicated to helping them do their job. It is powered by a group of experts that are passionate about innovation.</p>\r\n', '2015-11-01 00:00:00', 'A');

